trans-unit.source: Represents a designer verb that creates a template editing frame, and that can be invoked only by a template editor.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et designer verb som opprettes en mal for redigering, og som kan aktiveres bare av et redigeringsprogram for malen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateEditingVerb"></xref> class with the specified verb text and index.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateEditingVerb"> </xref> klassen med det angitte verbet og indeksen.

trans-unit.source: Expose templates through the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> property of a control designer.
trans-unit.target: Vise malene via den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>-egenskapen til en kontroll utformer.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>

trans-unit.source: The design host creates a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedEditableDesignerRegion> for each <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> defined for a control designer.
trans-unit.target: Utformingen verten oppretter en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedEditableDesignerRegion>for hver <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>definert for en kontroll utformer.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedEditableDesignerRegion>
